AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Calendar> "Calendar"@en)
EquivalentClasses(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Calendar> ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectIntersectionOf(DataSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#geo> xsd:anyURI) DataMaxCardinality(1 <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#geo>)) ObjectIntersectionOf(DataSomeValuesFrom(<http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#timeZone> xsd:string) DataMaxCardinality(1 <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#timeZone>))))

